  "detailed_description": "Command the Emerald Goblin Army, avenge and defeat the Ruby Goblin Army  and win the Great Gold War.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/35c801edc8803d68b8e502b521e0b757.webp?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br><br>Recruit special classes such as: Mages, Bombers, Barbarians, Necromancers and more. Call for precise artillery strikes to cause maximum destruction. Master <strong>Battles</strong> through 20 unique and increasingly difficult Campaign maps. Challenge yourself further in Freeplay <strong>Battles</strong> by selecting the highest difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/d21242e371e70722ae3924259f4ba983.avif?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=379 /></span><br><br>Enjoy a break from <strong>Battles</strong> and play a casual<strong> Mini-Game</strong>. Steal as much gold as possible from the enemy in Ruby Robbery, on your quest to steal a precious gem from the enemy. Face off against the entire \"Knights Gauntlet\" at once in a fierce battle. And more to come in the future.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/df45fb86b521fc2f00f7610b7fa5b991.webp?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br><strong><i>-Multiplayer Open BETA Available Now-</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/e8120f8f42484a05a56f57da0ae43da9.avif?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=270 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Command the Emerald Goblin Army, avenge and defeat the Ruby Goblin Army  and win the Great Gold War.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/35c801edc8803d68b8e502b521e0b757.webp?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br><br>Recruit special classes such as: Mages, Bombers, Barbarians, Necromancers and more. Call for precise artillery strikes to cause maximum destruction. Master <strong>Battles</strong> through 20 unique and increasingly difficult Campaign maps. Challenge yourself further in Freeplay <strong>Battles</strong> by selecting the highest difficulty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/d21242e371e70722ae3924259f4ba983.avif?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=379 /></span><br><br>Enjoy a break from <strong>Battles</strong> and play a casual<strong> Mini-Game</strong>. Steal as much gold as possible from the enemy in Ruby Robbery, on your quest to steal a precious gem from the enemy. Face off against the entire \"Knights Gauntlet\" at once in a fierce battle. And more to come in the future.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/df45fb86b521fc2f00f7610b7fa5b991.webp?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=56 /></span><br><strong><i>-Multiplayer Open BETA Available Now-</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301630/extras/e8120f8f42484a05a56f57da0ae43da9.avif?t=1708105616\" width=616 height=270 /></span>",
